metadata.name: The Hope
metadata.description:
The Beginning is the Genisis piece of the Humble beginnings collection. The piece shows that in the beginning everyone has hope, ambition,dreams and a motive. Everyone has a goal to accomplish and they work hard to achieve that goal many times people fail to get to there but the most important thing is not to lose hope and be motivated towords achieving bigger goal in life.

words in the work- 
महत्वाकांक्षी- ambitious 
सपने- dreams
Hope
動機- motivation
